{"tid":2143138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天主VS中共】天主教區發信學校：促使學生認識《港區國安法》","createTime":"2020-08-07T02:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T02:29:39.000Z","uid":115013,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"26aa0c38345da6ff45c98a564803e22c73485920","tid":2143138,"uid":115013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"天主教香港教區向天主教中小學的校監及校長發信。信中指，天主教學校的辦學團體是教育局的長期伙伴，學校應扮演正面角色，並建議學校由新學年起，引導學校教職員團隊，促使學生正確認識《港區國安法》及《國歌法》，培育學生對國民身份認同的正確觀念。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n教區亦指要確保學校政策足以防範校園政治化，不讓校園成為任何人單方宣傳政治訊息或訴求的場所。教區建議學校的名義一旦遭人利用，應立即公開澄清，以正視聽。"},{"pid":"a64007704d0c141f27d5905c546b8228c0814019","tid":2143138,"uid":115013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542257-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542257-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLBdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=7ffcb2b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542257-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5ed32b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542257-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d59ca4a4a7e98c9ed795df5330fd5c525231e78d","tid":2143138,"uid":115013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"天主已死 共匪極樂 淋奠有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}